16 NEW SECTION. Section 6. Midterm reports. (1) The commission shall compile a midterm report for
17 each judge relying on that judge's midterm evaluation. The midterm report may also be based on further
18 information the commission considers useful for purposes of judicial evaluation or self-improvement.
19 (2) The commission shall provide the midterm report to the evaluated judge, the Montana supreme
20 court, and the court administrator.
